<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV74">
<l>aṟintaṟintu vāmaṉaṉa ṭiyiṇaiva ṇaṅkiṉāṟ</l>
<l>ceṟinteḻunta ñāṉamōṭu celvamuñci ṟantiṭum</l>
<l>maṟinteḻunta teṇṭiraiyuṇ maṉṉumālai vāḻttiṉāṟ</l>
<l>paṟinteḻuntu tīviṉaikaḷ paṟṟaṟutaṟ pāṉmaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one worships the two feet of Vāmana knowing [He is the means]</l>
<l rend="indent">and knowing [He is the aim],</l>
<l>Wealth will abound, along with knowledge that grows in a dense way.</l>
<l>If one praises Māl who dwells on the clear waves that rise up,</l>
<l>It is natural that the grip of the evil karman that grows flowing out quickly should cease.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
